{"name":"Balanced Aid","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An ally within 30 feet damages an enemy or heals a creature.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You balance the energies of the battlefield. If your triggering ally damaged an enemy, you grant 2 + your level temporary Hit Points to an ally within 30 feet. They last until the next time you use Balanced Aid, up to a maximum of 1 minute.</p>\n<p>If your ally healed a creature, you deal force damage equal to 2 + your level to an enemy within 30 feet.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.bMRlmbpZwt7m9Sps"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679763305087,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"5WAz8VGsXFnGzfGi"}
{"name":"Aiding Strike","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An ally attempts a Strike against an enemy within your reach.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You join your blade in harmony with your ally&rsquo;s attack. Attempt a melee Strike against the enemy. On a hit, you also succeed at Aiding your ally&rsquo;s attack roll, and you critically succeed if your Strike was a critical hit.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ND4kxL7Q8nBaFtnt"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679750914150,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"5iTXRhxZOnKL0T9X"}
{"name":"Dervish Strike","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You or an ally critically hit an enemy and another enemy is within your reach.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You spin unexpectedly and attack the second enemy while their attention is distracted. Attempt a melee Strike against the second enemy. They are flat-footed against this Strike.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.kwcj1NPw1MgzvJAD"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679764021819,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"6PYmb5rcD16trBPb"}
{"name":"Grim Honor","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> <span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Calibri',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">An enemy enters into flanking position, Strikes while flanking, becomes invisible, or uses a skill action that requires a Deception or Stealth check. The enemy must begin this action within your reach or move into your reach during this action.</span></p>\n<hr>\n<p class=\"PF2StatBody\">You punish your foe for their impudent attempt at deception. Make a melee Strike against the target, resolving the attack roll before they complete their action and gain its benefits. In addition to the usual effects on a hit, the triggering creature takes a -2 circumstance penalty on the check. On a critical hit, the penalty increases to -4.</p>\n<p class=\"PF2StatBodyIndent\"><strong>Special</strong> If you have Attack of Opportunity, you gain an additional reaction each round you can use for Grim Honor.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.0Shm44nFuNyTyj5A"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1677895372180,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"9EL9UGZawxagyKyK"}
{"name":"Makeshift Shielding","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An ally within your reach takes damage.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You study the source of damage and begin cobbling together defenses against them. Choose one type of damage your ally has taken. They gain resistance to this damage equal to 2 + your level until the end of this combat. While this resistance lasts, you can spend an action with the manipulate trait to grant this same resistance to another ally within your reach with the same duration.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.wV2wrJjekihAEGKG"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679764136831,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"Cyy4TrMQdTSebYfB"}
{"name":"Glimpse of Pacifism","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An enemy damages your ally, and both are within 15 feet of you.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>Your foe hesitates as they consider the possibility of peace. The foe must choose one of the following options:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The enemy must not deal any damage until the end of their next turn. If they do, they become clumsy 2 for 1 round.</li>\n<li>The ally gains resistance to all damage against the triggering damage equal to 2 + your level. After the damaging effect is applied, the enemy becomes clumsy 2 until the end of its next turn.</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.KZM2TGdhNrtHIADf"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679750871562,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"D9RZqZhlLG2MPjcI"}
{"name":"Defy Burden","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An ally takes persistent damage (either initially or at the end of their turn) or gains a condition (other than dying or wounded) with a numerical value.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You offer solace amidst turmoil. Your ally may attempt a flat check to end the persistent damage or attempt a saving throw to reduce the condition&rsquo;s numerical value by 1. If the condition resulted from a failed saving throw, use the same type of saving throw. If not, use Fortitude for drained, enfeebled, sickened, slowed, or stunned; Reflex for clumsy; and Will for doomed, frightened, and stupefied.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7tuucB2lR5SInJAs"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679750698820,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"EC4UX9nM7s3isEyJ"}
{"name":"Impede Influence","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An ally within 15 feet is affected by an emotion or mental effect.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You ward your ally&rsquo;s mind and assail the attacker. The enemy who created the effect must choose one of the following options:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The ally is unaffected by the triggering effect.</li>\n<li>The ally gains resistance to all damage against the triggering effect equal to 2 + your level. After the effect is applied, the enemy becomes stupefied 2 until the end of its next turn.</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.7yIkh568DffzTP0E"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679750792987,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"FpUyg76TqgxmV6Qy"}
{"name":"Retributive Disarm","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> <span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Calibri',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">An enemy damages your ally, and both are within 15 feet of you.</span></p>\n<hr>\n<p class=\"PF2StatBody\">You protect your ally and strike your foe. The ally gains resistance to all damage against the triggering damage equal to 2 + your level. If the foe is within reach, attempt to Disarm it. You don&rsquo;t need a free hand to do so.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.r8UsOz7gCmaB1NTp"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1677895373415,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"GNtotxQerjjg33z6"}
{"name":"Retributive Tangle","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An enemy within 15 feet damages an ally.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You give the foe an opportunity to relent before invoking nature&rsquo;s wrath. You cast @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.uZK2BYzPnxUBnDjr]{Tanglefoot} as a divine cantrip, targeting the triggering enemy. Before you make your spell attack roll, they can choose to forego the triggering damage to make the outcome one degree worse.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.P0rX9pQahSPuwz74"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679762974202,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"Q64tLslJwSNsm1wq"}
{"name":"Ongoing Sting","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<section class=\"statblock\">\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> <span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Calibri',sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">An ally damages an enemy within 15 feet, or an enemy within 15 feet ends persistent damage they are affected by.</span></p>\n</section>\n<hr>\n<p>You declare the creature&rsquo;s suffering unfinished. The triggering enemy takes persistent damage equal to your level matching the triggering damage type. If there were multiple damage types, choose one. The creature then becomes immune to your Ongoing Sting for 1 minute.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.3qQVOdMUVQg8DHnB"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679750641456,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"Qqqf8x4NpILrp1sm"}
{"name":"Lingering Suffering","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An enemy within 15 feet succeeds at a flat check to end persistent damage or succeeds at a saving throw against an effect that deals damage.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You teach your foe the value of suffering. The triggering enemy must attempt the flat check or saving throw again and take the second result. They are then immune to your Lingering Suffering for 1 hour.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion","misfortune"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.x6Gqv5zUtypOWoVm"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679764238665,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"RMvzWzSuQA6YTfwv"}
{"name":"Life Sap","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An enemy damages an ally, and both are within 15 feet.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You intone tidings of the offender&rsquo;s coming demise. The foe must choose one of the following options:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The ally is unharmed by the triggering damage.</li>\n<li>The ally gains resistance to all damage against the triggering damage equal to 2 + your level. After the damaging effect is applied, the enemy becomes slowed 1. The slowed effect remains until the enemy spends an entire turn without harming the triggering ally.</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.faIbXpLDpdMfrAKN"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679763805652,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"WJvVQTYUi5FeFS2X"}
{"name":"Retributive Aid","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> Your ally within 15 feet misses on a Strike.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You cover your ally with prayer. Attempt to Aid your ally with an attack roll or Religion skill check, possibly changing the outcome. Regardless, your ally gains resistance equal to 2 + your level against all damage the next time they take damage before the start of their next turn.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.QYKw8CS4uiTuCOMt"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679763035745,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"YWqqO6EtALRFzeH6"}
{"name":"Boundless Destruction","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You damage an enemy within 15 feet and they are not reduced to 0 Hit Points.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You issue forth a torrent of destruction that seems to never end. The damaged creature chooses one of the following.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The damaged creature becomes stunned 1.</li>\n<li>The damaged creature takes persistent damage of the same type equal to your level. If this reaction was triggered by persistent damage you caused, you instead deal additional damage once equal to half your level rounded up.</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.fnI9M5trbFcvbBN7"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679763902569,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"fx42cMopiY0z7IHF"}
{"name":"Allied Extension","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> Your ally within 15 feet succeeds but doesn&rsquo;t critically succeed at an attack roll, and their target is within your reach.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You demonstrate the ways of perfection to your ally. Attempt a melee Strike against your ally&rsquo;s target. If you critically hit, your ally&rsquo;s multiple attack penalty from the triggering Strike is reduced by 1.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.S62cfRLPWSiQv1vM"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679763098433,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"jAX9i5WPI2OzUP7l"}
{"name":"Retributive Grasp","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An enemy within 15 feet damages you.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You capture your enemy&rsquo;s attention. The foe must choose one of the following options.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You take no damage, and the enemy loses the action.</li>\n<li>You gain resistance equal to 2 + your level against all triggering damage. The enemy becomes fascinated by you.</li>\n</ul>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.WpscnghlbMvGa1vI"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679763210259,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"pbbgDaHwZlR8b3Gm"}
{"name":"Shrouded Strike","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You deal damage to an enemy within 15 feet.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You retreat into cloying shadows. Attempt a Stealth check against the damaged enemy&rsquo;s Perception DC.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Success </strong>You become hidden to the damaged creature. Attempt another Strike against the damaged creature. Your multiple attack penalty applies and increases as usual. You don&rsquo;t lose the hidden condition because of this Strike.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> You become hidden to the damaged creature.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> You become concealed to the damaged creature.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure </strong>No effect.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.cGR6XL9PGaDsuK7t"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679763731361,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"x2OKWhqoV5bsnrIw"}
{"name":"Revelatory Glimpse","type":"action","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An enemy damages an ally, and both are within 15 feet.&nbsp;</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You interfere in the triggering attack and probe the enemy&rsquo;s tactics as you do so. The ally gains resistance to all damage against the triggering damage equal to 2 + your level. Attempt to Recall Knowledge about the enemy using Religion.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Divine Causes and Inquisitions"},"traits":{"value":["champion"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":null},"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":null},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp","effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.SOVmrUxn1AI49zTB"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1677895049877,"modifiedTime":1679764289537,"lastModifiedBy":"iQKsWqchZsLpvcle"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"yzhlo1GK7BclVrHs"}
